## 6. Error Handling

- Browser fails -> log "Error", skip browser, continue file steps
- JSON corrupt -> regenerate, log warning
- Submit fails -> don't log, retry next heartbeat
- Partial -> log what done, never skip step 5

---

## 7. Close Browser

`exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/close 2>&1`
Do not kill Chrome or `pkill`.

---

## 8. HEARTBEAT_OK

ALL must be true before returning HEARTBEAT_OK:
- No unread notifications (SS 3)
- All overdue tasks processed (SS 4)
- No pending tasks due within next 60min
- limits.json written with today's date (SS 1 + SS 5)
- Slack report outputted (SS 5)
- Browser closed (SS 7)
- Either: late night (23:00-08:00) with no tasks before 08:00, OR last heartbeat <30min ago
